  ('customs-6f0ba476-moex-00062', 'customs-6f0ba476', 'customs-6f0ba476-moex-113-f6c431ec', 'sub-customs-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'essay', '政府對於低所得者的補助可以採取現金補貼（cashsubsidy）或實物補貼
