  ('customs-6f0ba476-moex-00065', 'customs-6f0ba476', 'customs-6f0ba476-moex-112-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-customs-6f0ba476-02', NULL, 'essay', '甲在自己土地上建築 A屋一棟，全部工程由乙承包，現已完工，惟於施工
